⸻

1. Module Purpose

The Vault Management Module provides complete physical tracking of pledged jewellery and collateral items.

Every pledged asset must have a precise storage location from the moment it is accepted until it is redeemed or auctioned.

The module is responsible for:

* Vault Configuration
* Safe Management
* Tray Management
* Slot Management
* Asset Location Assignment
* Asset Retrieval
* Occupancy Tracking
* Vault Search
* Location History
* Insurance Mapping
* Compliance Tracking

