6. Core Business Rules

BR-VAULT-001

Every active Girvi must have a vault location.

BR-VAULT-002

A slot can contain only one active Girvi.

BR-VAULT-003

Location cannot be deleted.

BR-VAULT-004

All movements must be audited.

BR-VAULT-005

Redeemed Girvi automatically releases slot.

BR-VAULT-006

Auctioned Girvi automatically releases slot.

BR-VAULT-007

Insurance must cover every occupied vault.

BR-VAULT-008

Vault assignment mandatory before Girvi activation.

